race.description: Lees Orchard Tassie Golden Apple Pace
race.comment: HEZA PUNK ROCKER NZ (3) left the mainland with a Melton win last month and has completed a hat trick by toughing out narrow wins in his last two outings at this circuit. Switches back to a standing start but won under those conditions two back and should be hard to stop from the front mark. TRIEDTOTELLYA (10) came from this handicap and got within a nose of Heza Punk Rocker at this circuit and distance last start, his first outing since ending last campaign with a string of wins. Owns a strong strike rate here and his second-up record stands at two wins and two placings from four attempts so could progress enough to turn the tables. STAR MAJOR (12) added to his ultra consistent form when beaten a head here last Sunday. Starts from the 30m mark but was a standing start winner last month. MAEBEE (4) will be fitter for the resuming second.
